# nexus /.chain — chain definitions (raw#0 forward-chain)
# Mirrors hexa-lang /.chain schema (3-repo convergence).
# Created 2026-04-27.
#
# Format:
#   chain <id> <status> "<name>"
#     step.<id>.cmd <command...>
#     step.<id>.timeout <seconds>     (optional, default 600)
#     mode <strict|loose>             (default strict)
#     ttl  <seconds>                  (default 3600)
#     why  <text>
#
# Semantics (enforced by tool/chain_runner.hexa via hexa-lang):
#   · user triggers any step; downstream steps then auto-cascade
#   · strict mode requires all earlier step_<id>_ok markers to exist
#   · loose mode skips prev-marker check (entry from any step)
#   · marker files live under .chain-state/<chain_id>/ — chflags uchg locked
#   · any step failure cancels the remaining downstream cascade.

chain 1 live "kick-cascade — kick run → witness lint → atlas absorb → roadmap sync"
  step.kick.cmd HEXA_RESOLVER_NO_REROUTE=1 HEXA_SHIM_NO_DARWIN_LANDING=1 nexus kick run "$TOPIC" --stratum "$STRATUM" --axes "$AXES" --noise alpha,beta,gamma --backend "$BACKEND" --parent-sid "$PARENT_SID"
  step.witness_lint.cmd hexa /Users/ghost/core/hexa-lang/hexa tool/witness_emit.hexa --selftest
  step.absorb.cmd hexa /Users/ghost/core/hexa-lang/hexa tool/atlas_absorb_lint.hexa
  step.roadmap.cmd hexa /Users/ghost/core/hexa-lang/hexa tool/roadmap_engine.hexa --reconcile
  mode strict
  ttl 7200
  why kick = atomic ω-cycle. cascade 가 atlas absorb + roadmap sync 보장. .own atlas-absorb-mandatory 가 step 3 의 backbone.

chain 2 live "daily-atlas-health — atlas drift + orphan witness 일일 점검"
  step.atlas_health.cmd hexa /Users/ghost/core/hexa-lang/hexa tool/atlas_health.hexa --quick
  step.absorb_lint.cmd hexa /Users/ghost/core/hexa-lang/hexa tool/atlas_absorb_lint.hexa
  step.drift_scan.cmd hexa /Users/ghost/core/hexa-lang/hexa tool/drift_scanner.hexa --domain nexus
  step.health_audit.cmd hexa /Users/ghost/core/hexa-lang/hexa tool/atlas_meta_dashboard.hexa --emit-jsonl
  mode strict
  ttl 3600
  why launchd 매일 트리거. orphan witness + atlas drift + meta dashboard refresh 일괄.

chain 3 live "drill-cascade — drill batch → falsifier seal → roadmap update"
  step.drill_batch.cmd hexa /Users/ghost/core/hexa-lang/hexa tool/drill_batch.hexa --criteria "$CRITERIA" --seeds "$SEEDS"
  step.falsifier_seal.cmd hexa /Users/ghost/core/hexa-lang/hexa tool/drill_breakthrough_runner.hexa --seal
  step.roadmap_update.cmd hexa /Users/ghost/core/hexa-lang/hexa tool/roadmap_engine.hexa --reconcile-drill
  mode strict
  ttl 7200
  why drill batch (T3→T4 85→95% breakthrough criteria) 의 결과를 falsifier 평가 + roadmap 으로 환류.

chain 4 live "kick-recover — kick failure 시 retire + re-fire 후속 cascade"
  step.retire_witnesses.cmd hexa /Users/ghost/core/hexa-lang/hexa tool/witness_emit.hexa --status archived --reason "$REASON"
  step.regenerate.cmd nexus kick tree
  step.refire.cmd HEXA_RESOLVER_NO_REROUTE=1 HEXA_SHIM_NO_DARWIN_LANDING=1 nexus kick run "$TOPIC" --stratum "$STRATUM" --axes "$AXES" --noise alpha,beta,gamma --backend "$BACKEND" --parent-sid "$PARENT_SID"
  mode strict
  ttl 3600
  why workflow violation (axes/falsifier/parent-sid 누락) 발생 시 archive → tree 재조회 → 정상 재발사. 2026-04-27 incident 기반.

